    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>School</strong>&nbsp;abjuration&nbsp;[good];\n    <strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;inquisitor 4, paladin 3;\n    \n    \n    \n    \n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Casting Time</strong>&nbsp;1 standard action<br>\n    <strong>Components</strong>&nbsp;V, S<br>\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Range</strong>&nbsp;touch<br>\n    \n    <strong>Targets</strong>&nbsp;armor touched<br>\n    \n    <strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;1 minute/level<br>\n    <strong>Saving Throw</strong>&nbsp;Will negates (harmless, object);&nbsp;<strong>Spell Resistance</strong>&nbsp;yes<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  <p>You imbue your armor with a righteous aura. It gains a +1 enhancement bonus per four caster levels (maximum +5 at 20th level). When using your judgment or smite ability, you gain DR 5/evil.</p><p>An outfit of regular clothing counts as armor that grants no AC bonus for the purpose of this spell.</p>\n</div>\n",
